forms down the side of the pulpit each side, right across, you know, there used to be full with peo-, children, and when the minister used to come in, it always used to be a little bit amusing for us when the minister come in for the vestry, h
e came in, he might come in the back door, and, er, the girls who were sitting on the top had to stand up and let him get past, that always used to be a little bit amu-; oh, wonderful days, and if you'd been at the one I was at three weeks ago, my dear, t
hey were wonderful days the anniversaries. Lovely times.
