r
-, last night. He came to take the service that morning and I walked down, I used to get a ride a good bit, but I didn't get a ride because the lady who used to take me was ill, and I walked over. Not near so many, there wan't about twenty people there, a
nd the children, there were maybe might have been twenty children, I don't know, anyhow, and the minister come in, and right at the corner there was boy there with one, do you know these here pop }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3280237\charrsid8142759 music\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6165194\charrsid8142759  they play. My dear, that was ridiculous in the church. I was disgusted with it. (..) \{BLANK\}
