et another preacher. I said, oh well, he said, that's all right, though, he said, you can come. Well, do you know what a stupid thing I done, I just spoke to one or two people and got outside and I thought, no, I don't think I'll go. Well, this young lady
 who I spoke to, I said, Barbara, will you go and tell the Reverend (..) \{BLANK\}
