\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5185091 AL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6165194\charrsid8142759 Yes, I did for several years, and then, er,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15426346 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6165194\charrsid8142759 Did you teach, before you got married, in Sunday School?
