Yes, I didn't get on very well with it. I wasn't very well, 'cause unfortunately I had a breakdown after I got, after I'd been married a while, nervous breakdown, I really was ill, and, er, I did it for a little while, and I lost my 
pail I lost this, that and the other, and my husband went down to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5597594\charrsid8142759 Fi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6165194\charrsid8142759 
eld and got me and said don't you do that any more, and I did go to the Scotch people once or twice; I used to go, well, I used to go and stop for the day sometimes, while they went ou
